    <title>SchoolMan | Online School Management Systems </title>
    <!--Meta-->
    <meta name="description" content="SchoolMan is a complete management application for school administration, teachers and parents, it provides a web as well as mobile application which can be downloaded from Google Play store. The mobile application will be customized to the particular school with school name. SchoolMan handles all your school activities by integrating the functionalities of school administration, teachers and communication with parents. It is also associated with a real time GPS tracking system for school bus which ensures safety and timely transit of students.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Schoolman, class management software, school management softwarpromotestudentse, class software, School software, web based school management system, online school management systems, school management software, school management system, Online School Tutorial, Online school payment, school fee payment, timetable, schedule, timetable software, school scheduling">
    <meta name="author" content="SchoolMan">
